src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自從七一 連登已經有好多好多白色恐怖既post<br />\n無論係琴晚柴灣事件、今日有人開post話十幾個cid拉人、俾人爆門、定班狗今日開既直播都好<br />\n<br />\n大家要暫時停一停，諗一諗<br />\n呢一連串事件有冇關聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加上不斷有手足話去自殺<br />\n唔好話我黑心定點<br />\n真係唔排除有狗想引人出黎借機求其拉幾條友返去交差<br />\n<br />\n今日睇到朋友以上既文章<br />\n真係有啲擔心我地會俾佢地班小人製造既恐慌而自亂陣腳<br />\n同時亦覺得 假如人地滅聲之先 我地已先行滅聲<br />\n咁今日呢個香港就正正成為送中後既香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然 有任何不利自己既物件絕對支持換過批新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但唔好太過恐懼於白色恐怖中而令我地成為一盤散沙<br />\n敵人就係鬥唔過我地先要用埋呢啲招數<br />\n<br />\n仲有記得要fact check <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未經證實盡量唔好傳住<br />\n免得釀成<span style=\"font-size: large;\">「狼來了」</span>事件<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思講到1999<br />\n希望大家記住自己既初衷<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">一齊黎，一齊走<br />\n一齊上，一齊落</span></span><br />\n<br />\n真係不幸被捕既人<br />\n記住唔好諗太多！！！<br />\n請參考以下post<br />\n<br />\n萬一比人拉 千祈唔好亂 我敢講一定冇事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1282154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1282154</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我地咁多位手足係同一個人黎 冇得分割<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>We Stand As One </strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:27:26.000Z","msg":"巴打心水清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對住共產黨最緊要係團結，冷靜，堅持<br />\n只要大家心入面都有同一個信念<br />\n維尼都會好撚驚"},{"pid":"d08d3006e6e22e7058dfd1df90f8192404907543","tid":1282786,"uid":105353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:27:56.000Z","msg":"我無野講<br />\n我要見律師<br />\n我要飲水<br />\n我要食飯<br />\n我要毛氈<br />\n我有權唔unlock 電話"},{"pid":"d4b6678af0ea854c901c88ce80becdeffa78a53d","tid":1282786,"uid":67491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:37:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6c35fe8b900956ccd5c1cd138c363980c977ed75","tid":1282786,"uid":43082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:43:54.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"466c264f4c8df325b6c5ce289faba2a3be5990d4","tid":1282786,"uid":43082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:44:40.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"2649c305c67dcb9e10d8a2990fcc8779ebc87f52","tid":1282786,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:46:35.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"72c4d29931a88290ec10a079ab9b8c0a4512cf27","tid":1282786,"uid":74958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:48:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我無嘢講</span>"},{"pid":"4b6a4bcab17921cade4b6bed30760c6f3af9a972","tid":1282786,"uid":74958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:49:00.000Z","msg":"我無野講<br />\n我要見律師<br />\n我要飲水<br />\n我要食飯<br />\n我要毛氈<br />\n我有權唔unlock 電話"},{"pid":"ec822464e70c6f81c99d7e3daf057cae866ff951","tid":1282786,"uid":259820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:50:48.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"cb0f28dcf8e278e6d67be55de09186d0c824bdea","tid":1282786,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:51:21.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"4d967947a829e5ac2be8576001abb08c33c7c713","tid":1282786,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:52:43.000Z","msg":"試著說<br />\n我無野講<br />\n唔使理會佢講咩<br />\n唔好比佢氹到<br />\n唔使認罪<br />\n我要見律師<br />\n唔好比佢大到<img src=\"/